pounce.

09:11.300 --> 09:12.468
[SIGHS]

09:12.468 --> 09:14.136
Hey, Timmy.

09:14.887 --> 09:16.263
Morning, sir.

09:16.263 --> 09:19.100
Aw, come here.

09:19.516 --> 09:22.979
