you little freak?

09:26.816 --> 09:28.735
I beg your pardon, sir?

09:28.735 --> 09:32.196
I mean, what happened,
little buddy? Talk to me.

09:32.196 --> 09:33.114
I just froze.

09:33.114 --> 09:35.157
I mean, I don't want
to get married,

09:35.157 --> 09:37.493
but I've never broken
up with anyone before.

09:37.493 --> 09:39.996
