and get dumped. Don't be crazy.

11:09.085 --> 11:09.919
Fine, I won't even react.

11:09.919 --> 11:13.464
Even though my whole world
is crashing down.

11:13.464 --> 11:16.050
Suneetha, I'm so sorry,
I didn't mean it.

11:16.050 --> 11:17.384
We'll make it work.

11:17.384 --> 11:18.385
Oh, Timmy.

11:18.385 --> 11:20.137
No, no, no.

11:20.137 --> 11:22.681
Timmy, stand there.

11:23.349 --> 11:24.809
Sit down. Please.

11:24.809 --> 11:26.685
It's not that complicated.

11:26.685 --> 11:28.771
All right.

11:28.771 --> 11:29.605
Suneetha,

11:29.605 --> 11:32.524
